estors unless the manager is registered in the EU. One carve-out to this re=
gulation is =93reverse solicitation=94 meaning we must prove that Vestar an=
d our agent (in this case you) did not reach out directly to this investor =
to solicit an investment into our fund.

In order to prove =93reverse solicitation=94 we must have Tamar Marash sign=
 the attached addendum. In addition to this document, this investor will ne=
ed to be =93opted-up=94 to a professional client status from retail client =
status to avoid Vestar having to produce additional fund documentation. I h=
ave attached the =93professional opt-up=94 pack here, which provides a =93q=
uantitative test=94 for the investor. The investor must meet two of these r=
equirements in order to qualify for the =93opt-up.=94

Please let me know how you would like to handle. We have not been directly =
in contact with this investor so these requests will need to be communicate=
d to The Service.

